{
  "video_id": "IL2lb9fmIV8",
  "title": "The deadly legacy of cluster bombs | Laura Boushnak",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 12809.0,
      "end_time": 14982.0,
      "text": "I once had this nightmare:"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 15700.0,
      "end_time": 18908.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m standing in the middle of a deserted field full of land mines."
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 19571.0,
      "end_time": 22360.0,
      "text": "In real life, I love to hike,"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 22600.0,
      "end_time": 25729.0,
      "text": "but every time I want to go on a hike, it makes me nervous."
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 26327.0,
      "end_time": 28851.0,
      "text": "I have this thought in the back of my mind"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 28875.0,
      "end_time": 30389.0,
      "text": "that I might lose a limb."
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 31402.0,
      "end_time": 34101.0,
      "text": "This underlying fear started 10 years ago,"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 34125.0,
      "end_time": 37423.0,
      "text": "after I met Mohammed, a cluster bomb survivor"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 37447.0,
      "end_time": 41383.0,
      "text": "of the summer 2006 Israel-Hezbollah War in Lebanon."
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 42303.0,
      "end_time": 45556.0,
      "text": "Mohammed, like so many other survivors all around the world,"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 45581.0,
      "end_time": 50568.0,
      "text": "had to live through the horrifying repercussions of cluster munitions"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 50592.0,
      "end_time": 52184.0,
      "text": "on a daily basis."
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 53122.0,
      "end_time": 55761.0,
      "text": "When the one-month conflict started in Lebanon,"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 55785.0,
      "end_time": 59980.0,
      "text": "I was still working at Agence France-Presse in Paris."
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 59837.0,
      "end_time": 62439.0,
      "text": "I remember how I was glued to the screens,"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 62463.0,
      "end_time": 64647.0,
      "text": "anxiously following the news."
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 65155.0,
      "end_time": 66838.0,
      "text": "I wanted to reassure myself"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 66862.0,
      "end_time": 69741.0,
      "text": "that the falling bombs missed my parents&#39; home."
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 70773.0,
      "end_time": 74311.0,
      "text": "When I arrived in Beirut on assignment to cover that war,"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 74335.0,
      "end_time": 76803.0,
      "text": "I was relieved to be united with my family,"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 76827.0,
      "end_time": 79950.0,
      "text": "after they had finally managed to escape southern Lebanon."
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 80744.0,
      "end_time": 82543.0,
      "text": "The day the war was over,"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 82567.0,
      "end_time": 84717.0,
      "text": "I remember seeing this image --"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 84742.0,
      "end_time": 86185.0,
      "text": "one of blocked roads,"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 86209.0,
      "end_time": 90338.0,
      "text": "of displaced people eagerly rushing south, back to their homes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 90362.0,
      "end_time": 92457.0,
      "text": "regardless of what they would find."
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 93374.0,
      "end_time": 96443.0,
      "text": "An estimated four million cluster submunitions"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 96468.0,
      "end_time": 100104.0,
      "text": "were spread in Lebanon during the 34-day conflict."
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 102462.0,
      "end_time": 106100.0,
      "text": "Mohammed lost both legs during the last week of the conflict."
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 106826.0,
      "end_time": 109877.0,
      "text": "The fact that he lives a five-minute drive from my parents&#39; home"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 109901.0,
      "end_time": 112655.0,
      "text": "made it easier to follow him through the years."
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 112680.0,
      "end_time": 115660.0,
      "text": "It was now almost 10 years since we first met."
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 116309.0,
      "end_time": 117860.0,
      "text": "I saw the young boy"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 117884.0,
      "end_time": 121764.0,
      "text": "who had to endure physical and emotional trauma."
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 122277.0,
      "end_time": 125609.0,
      "text": "I saw the teenager who tried to offer his friends tattoos,"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 125633.0,
      "end_time": 128186.0,
      "text": "in return for a set fee of five dollars."
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 129169.00000000001,
      "end_time": 133313.0,
      "text": "And I know the young, jobless man who spends hours surfing the Internet"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 133337.0,
      "end_time": 136429.0,
      "text": "trying to meet a girl who might become his girlfriend."
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 137408.0,
      "end_time": 140922.0,
      "text": "His fate and the effects of losing his legs"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 140946.0,
      "end_time": 142943.0,
      "text": "are now his daily reality."
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 143578.0,
      "end_time": 145967.0,
      "text": "Survivors of bomb trauma like Mohammed"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 145991.0,
      "end_time": 149444.0,
      "text": "have to deal with so many details that never occur to us."
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 149817.0,
      "end_time": 150993.0,
      "text": "Who would have imagined"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 151170.0,
      "end_time": 153752.0,
      "text": "that so many daily tasks we do or take for granted,"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 153776.0,
      "end_time": 158290.0,
      "text": "such as going to the beach or even picking up something from the floor,"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 158530.0,
      "end_time": 161770.0,
      "text": "would become sources of stress and anxiety?"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 161886.0,
      "end_time": 164197.0,
      "text": "Well, that&#39;s what eventually became of Mohammed,"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 164221.0,
      "end_time": 166963.0,
      "text": "due to his inflexible prosthetic legs."
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 168465.0,
      "end_time": 172135.0,
      "text": "Ten years ago, I had no clue what a cluster bomb was,"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 172159.0,
      "end_time": 174447.0,
      "text": "nor its horrifying implications."
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 174835.0,
      "end_time": 177272.0,
      "text": "I learned that this indiscriminate weapon was used"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 177296.0,
      "end_time": 178810.0,
      "text": "in so many parts of the world"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 178835.0,
      "end_time": 181107.0,
      "text": "and continues to kill on a regular basis,"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 181131.0,
      "end_time": 184170.0,
      "text": "without distinguishing between a military target"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 184194.0,
      "end_time": 185366.0,
      "text": "or a child."
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 186141.0,
      "end_time": 187982.0,
      "text": "I naively asked myself,"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 188600.0,
      "end_time": 191385.0,
      "text": "\"But seriously, who made those weapons?"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 191847.0,
      "end_time": 193200.0,
      "text": "And what for?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 193687.0,
      "end_time": 196155.0,
      "text": "Let me explain to you what a cluster bomb is."
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 196179.0,
      "end_time": 199353.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s a large canister filled with bomblets."
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 199377.0,
      "end_time": 201400.0,
      "text": "When it&#39;s dropped from the air,"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 201640.0,
      "end_time": 205164.0,
      "text": "it opens up in midair to release hundreds of bomblets."
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 205632.0,
      "end_time": 207750.0,
      "text": "They scatter around wide areas"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 207774.0,
      "end_time": 208927.0,
      "text": "and on impact,"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 208951.0,
      "end_time": 210634.0,
      "text": "many fail to explode."
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 211348.0,
      "end_time": 214569.0,
      "text": "Those unexploded ones end up just like landmines --"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 214593.0,
      "end_time": 215826.0,
      "text": "sitting on the ground,"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 215850.0,
      "end_time": 217821.0,
      "text": "waiting for their next target."
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 218560.0,
      "end_time": 221140.0,
      "text": "If someone steps on them by accident"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 221380.0,
      "end_time": 222196.0,
      "text": "or picks them up,"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 222220.0,
      "end_time": 223678.0,
      "text": "they can explode."
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 224283.0,
      "end_time": 227166.0,
      "text": "These weapons are extremely unpredictable,"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 227190.0,
      "end_time": 229219.0,
      "text": "which makes the threat even bigger."
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 229243.0,
      "end_time": 232341.0,
      "text": "One day, a farmer can work his land without a problem."
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 232366.0,
      "end_time": 236321.0,
      "text": "The next day, he can make fire and burn some branches,"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 236345.0,
      "end_time": 240135.0,
      "text": "and the submunitions close by could be set off because of the heat."
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 240762.0,
      "end_time": 244311.0,
      "text": "The problem is children mistake those bomblets for toys,"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 244335.0,
      "end_time": 247686.0,
      "text": "because they can look like bouncy balls or soda cans."
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 248943.0,
      "end_time": 250809.0,
      "text": "Being a documentary photographer,"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 250833.0,
      "end_time": 254972.0,
      "text": "I decided to go back to Lebanon a few months after the conflict ended"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 254996.0,
      "end_time": 256969.0,
      "text": "to meet cluster bomb survivors."
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 256993.0,
      "end_time": 258144.0,
      "text": "And I met a few --"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 258168.0,
      "end_time": 259741.0,
      "text": "Hussein and Rasha,"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 259765.0,
      "end_time": 261765.0,
      "text": "who both lost a leg to submunitions."
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 262142.0,
      "end_time": 266359.0,
      "text": "Their stories are similar to so many other kids&#39; stories across the world"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 266383.0,
      "end_time": 269431.0,
      "text": "and are a testimony to the horrifying implications"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 269456.0,
      "end_time": 272286.0,
      "text": "of the continuous use of such weapons."
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 273332.0,
      "end_time": 276917.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s when I met Mohammed, in January 2007."
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 277427.0,
      "end_time": 278707.0,
      "text": "He was 11 years old,"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 278731.0,
      "end_time": 282245.0,
      "text": "and I met him exactly four months after his accident."
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 282777.0,
      "end_time": 283928.0,
      "text": "When I first saw him,"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 283952.0,
      "end_time": 286710.0,
      "text": "he was going through painful physiotherapy"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 286950.0,
      "end_time": 288710.0,
      "text": "to recover from his fresh wounds."
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 288547.0,
      "end_time": 290819.0,
      "text": "Still in shock at such a young age,"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 290843.0,
      "end_time": 294337.0,
      "text": "Mohammed was struggling to get used to his new body."
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 294650.0,
      "end_time": 298960.0,
      "text": "He would even wake up sometimes at night wanting to scratch his lost feet."
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 300187.0,
      "end_time": 303876.0,
      "text": "What drew me closer to his story was my instant realization"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 303900.0,
      "end_time": 307465.0,
      "text": "of the difficulties Mohammed was likely to face in the future --"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 307997.0,
      "end_time": 311322.0,
      "text": "that what he has been suffering while adjusting to his injury"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 311346.0,
      "end_time": 313160.0,
      "text": "at the age of 11,"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 313400.0,
      "end_time": 314656.0,
      "text": "would increase manyfold."
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 315771.0,
      "end_time": 317361.0,
      "text": "Even before his disability,"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 317385.0,
      "end_time": 319602.0,
      "text": "Mohammed&#39;s life wasn&#39;t easy."
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 319626.0,
      "end_time": 322905.0,
      "text": "He was born in the Rashidieh Camp for Palestinian refugees,"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 322930.0,
      "end_time": 325790.0,
      "text": "and this is where he still lives."
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 325103.0,
      "end_time": 328825.0,
      "text": "Lebanon holds some 400,000 Palestinian refugees,"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 328849.0,
      "end_time": 331147.0,
      "text": "and they suffer from discriminatory laws."
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 331662.0,
      "end_time": 334234.0,
      "text": "They&#39;re not allowed to work in the public sector"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 334259.0,
      "end_time": 336242.0,
      "text": "or practice certain professions"
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 336266.0,
      "end_time": 339254.0,
      "text": "and are denied the right to own property."
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 339278.0,
      "end_time": 340533.0,
      "text": "This is one of the reasons"
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 340557.0,
      "end_time": 343300.0,
      "text": "why Mohammed doesn&#39;t really regret dropping out of school"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 343324.0,
      "end_time": 344996.0,
      "text": "right after his injury."
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 345397.0,
      "end_time": 348936.0,
      "text": "He said, \"What&#39;s the point of a university degree"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 348960.0,
      "end_time": 351123.0,
      "text": "when I can&#39;t find a job to start with?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 353460.0,
      "end_time": 357260.0,
      "text": "Cluster bomb use creates a vicious circle of impact on communities,"
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 357284.0,
      "end_time": 359969.0,
      "text": "and not only the lives of their victims."
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 359993.0,
      "end_time": 363808.0,
      "text": "Many who get injured by this weapon drop out of school,"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 363832.0,
      "end_time": 366269.0,
      "text": "can&#39;t find jobs or even lose their jobs,"
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 366293.0,
      "end_time": 369490.0,
      "text": "therefore losing the ability to provide for their families."
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 369887.0,
      "end_time": 373214.0,
      "text": "This is not to mention the continuous physical pain"
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 373238.0,
      "end_time": 376343.0,
      "text": "and the experience of feeling isolated."
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 377512.0,
      "end_time": 380600.0,
      "text": "These weapons affect the poorest of the poor."
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 380624.0,
      "end_time": 383503.0,
      "text": "The high medical cost is a burden to the families."
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 383884.0,
      "end_time": 386931.0,
      "text": "They end up relying on humanitarian agencies,"
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 386955.0,
      "end_time": 389484.0,
      "text": "which is insufficient and unsustainable,"
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 389508.0,
      "end_time": 393150.0,
      "text": "especially when injuries require lifelong support to the injured."
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 393704.0,
      "end_time": 395542.0,
      "text": "Ten years after Mohammed&#39;s injury,"
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 395566.0,
      "end_time": 399284.0,
      "text": "he is still unable to afford proper prosthetic legs."
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 399856.0,
      "end_time": 401661.0,
      "text": "He&#39;s very cautious with his steps,"
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 401685.0,
      "end_time": 403703.0,
      "text": "as a couple of falls over the years"
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 403727.0,
      "end_time": 406147.0,
      "text": "brought him embarrassment among his friends."
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 407218.0,
      "end_time": 409297.0,
      "text": "He joked that since he doesn&#39;t have legs,"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 409321.0,
      "end_time": 411977.0,
      "text": "some days he tries to walk on his hands."
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 413540.0,
      "end_time": 416412.0,
      "text": "One of the worst yet invisible impacts of the weapon"
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 416436.0,
      "end_time": 418988.0,
      "text": "is the psychological scars it leaves."
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 419348.0,
      "end_time": 421664.0,
      "text": "In one of Mohammed&#39;s early medical reports,"
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 421688.0,
      "end_time": 424731.0,
      "text": "he was diagnosed with signs of PTSD."
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 424755.0,
      "end_time": 429987.0,
      "text": "He suffered from anxiety, poor appetite, sleep disturbance"
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 430110.0,
      "end_time": 432422.0,
      "text": "and showed signs of anger."
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 433197.0,
      "end_time": 437811.0,
      "text": "The reality is Mohammed never received proper help to fully recover."
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 438271.0,
      "end_time": 442487.0,
      "text": "His current obsession is to leave Lebanon at any cost --"
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 442511.0,
      "end_time": 445376.0,
      "text": "even if it meant embarking on a hazardous journey"
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 445400.0,
      "end_time": 449979.0,
      "text": "along with refugees drifting towards Europe today through the Mediterranean."
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 451340.0,
      "end_time": 453295.0,
      "text": "Knowing how risky such a journey would be,"
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 453319.0,
      "end_time": 456439.0,
      "text": "he said, \"If I were to die on the way,"
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 456463.0,
      "end_time": 457723.0,
      "text": "it doesn&#39;t matter.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 457747.0,
      "end_time": 460863.0,
      "text": "To Mohammed, he is dead here, anyway."
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 462294.0,
      "end_time": 465301.0,
      "text": "Cluster bombs are a world problem,"
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 465326.0,
      "end_time": 469987.0,
      "text": "as this munition keeps destroying and hurting whole communities"
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 470110.0,
      "end_time": 471714.0,
      "text": "for generations to come."
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 472618.0,
      "end_time": 476132.0,
      "text": "In an online interview with the director of the Mines Advisory Group,"
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 476156.0,
      "end_time": 477307.0,
      "text": "Jamie Franklin,"
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 477331.0,
      "end_time": 478487.0,
      "text": "he said,"
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 478511.0,
      "end_time": 483630.0,
      "text": "\"The US forces dropped over two million tons of munitions over Laos."
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 483570.0,
      "end_time": 486255.0,
      "text": "If they couldn&#39;t find their targets in Vietnam,"
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 486279.0,
      "end_time": 490576.0,
      "text": "there were free-drop areas in Laos where planes would drop their loads"
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 490600.0,
      "end_time": 492595.0,
      "text": "before going back to base,"
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 492619.0,
      "end_time": 495656.0,
      "text": "because it&#39;s dangerous to land with loaded planes.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 496653.0,
      "end_time": 499415.0,
      "text": "According to the International Committee of the Red Cross,"
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 499439.0,
      "end_time": 502795.0,
      "text": "in Laos alone -- one of the poorest countries in the world --"
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 502819.0,
      "end_time": 507632.0,
      "text": "nine to 27 million unexploded submunitions remain."
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 508238.0,
      "end_time": 513171.0,
      "text": "Some 11,000 people have been killed or injured since 1973."
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 514691.00000000006,
      "end_time": 519579.00000000006,
      "text": "This lethal weapon has been used by over 20 states during armed conflicts"
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 519602.0,
      "end_time": 521760.0,
      "text": "in over 35 countries,"
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 521784.0,
      "end_time": 525213.0,
      "text": "such as Ukraine, Iraq and Sudan."
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 526403.0,
      "end_time": 530689.0,
      "text": "So far, 119 states have joined an international treaty"
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 530713.0,
      "end_time": 532424.0,
      "text": "banning cluster bombs,"
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 532448.0,
      "end_time": 535487.0,
      "text": "which is officially called the Convention on Cluster Munitions."
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 536417.0,
      "end_time": 539867.0,
      "text": "But some of the biggest producers of cluster munitions --"
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 539891.0,
      "end_time": 543230.0,
      "text": "namely, the United States, Russia and China --"
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 543254.0,
      "end_time": 545724.0,
      "text": "remain outside of this lifesaving treaty"
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 545748.0,
      "end_time": 547685.0,
      "text": "and continue to produce them,"
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 547709.0,
      "end_time": 550527.0,
      "text": "reserve the right to produce them in the future,"
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 550552.0,
      "end_time": 553278.0,
      "text": "keep those harmful weapons in their stockpiles"
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 553302.0,
      "end_time": 556490.0,
      "text": "and even possibly use them in the future."
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 557520.0,
      "end_time": 561712.0,
      "text": "Cluster bombs have reportedly been used most recently"
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 561736.0,
      "end_time": 565122.0,
      "text": "in the ongoing conflicts in Yemen and Syria."
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 566122.0,
      "end_time": 568885.0,
      "text": "According to research on the worldwide investments"
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 568909.0,
      "end_time": 570535.0,
      "text": "in cluster munitions producers"
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 570559.0,
      "end_time": 572641.0,
      "text": "by Pax, a Dutch-based NGO,"
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 573380.0,
      "end_time": 577256.0,
      "text": "financial institutions invested billions of US dollars"
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 577280.0,
      "end_time": 580630.0,
      "text": "into companies that make cluster munitions."
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 580660.0,
      "end_time": 584507.0,
      "text": "The majority of these institutions are based in countries"
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 584532.0,
      "end_time": 588530.0,
      "text": "that have not yet signed the Convention on Cluster Munitions."
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 589114.0,
      "end_time": 591141.0,
      "text": "Getting back to Mohammed,"
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 591165.0,
      "end_time": 594814.0,
      "text": "one of the few jobs he was able to find was picking lemons."
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 595505.0,
      "end_time": 599670.0,
      "text": "When I ask him if it&#39;s safe to work in the field he said,"
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 599910.0,
      "end_time": 600300.0,
      "text": "\"I&#39;m not sure.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 601210.0,
      "end_time": 605690.0,
      "text": "Research shows that cluster munitions often contaminate areas"
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 605715.0,
      "end_time": 608957.0,
      "text": "where agriculture is the main source of income."
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 610140.0,
      "end_time": 612890.0,
      "text": "According to Handicap International&#39;s research,"
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 612914.0,
      "end_time": 618891.0,
      "text": "98 percent of those killed or injured by cluster munitions are civilians."
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 619479.0,
      "end_time": 622689.0,
      "text": "Eighty-four percent of casualties are males."
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 623740.0,
      "end_time": 625806.0,
      "text": "In countries where these people have no choice"
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 625831.0,
      "end_time": 627887.0,
      "text": "but to work in those fields,"
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 627911.0,
      "end_time": 629566.0,
      "text": "they simply do it"
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 629591.0,
      "end_time": 630823.0,
      "text": "and risk it."
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 631914.0,
      "end_time": 634982.0,
      "text": "Mohammed is the only male to three sisters."
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 635600.0,
      "end_time": 638332.0,
      "text": "Culturally, he&#39;s expected to provide for his family,"
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 638356.0,
      "end_time": 639765.0,
      "text": "but he simply can&#39;t."
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 640117.0,
      "end_time": 642200.0,
      "text": "He tried to have so many different jobs,"
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 642225.0,
      "end_time": 645791.0,
      "text": "but he couldn&#39;t keep any due to his physical disability"
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 645815.0,
      "end_time": 649280.0,
      "text": "and the less-than-friendly environment to people with disabilities,"
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 649304.0,
      "end_time": 650525.0,
      "text": "to say the least."
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 651583.0,
      "end_time": 654911.0,
      "text": "It hurts him a lot when he goes out looking for a job,"
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 654935.0,
      "end_time": 656127.0,
      "text": "and he&#39;s turned away"
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 656152.0,
      "end_time": 658817.0,
      "text": "with a small amount of money paid to him out of pity."
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 659650.0,
      "end_time": 662381.0,
      "text": "He said, \"I&#39;m not here to beg for money,"
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 662405.0,
      "end_time": 664113.0,
      "text": "I just want to earn it.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 665764.0,
      "end_time": 668182.0,
      "text": "Mohammed today is 21 years old."
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 668206.0,
      "end_time": 669404.0,
      "text": "He&#39;s illiterate,"
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 669428.0,
      "end_time": 672497.0,
      "text": "and he communicates with voice messages."
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 672521.0,
      "end_time": 674274.0,
      "text": "Here is one of his messages."
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 675234.0,
      "end_time": 680209.0,
      "text": "(Audio) Mohammed: (Speaking in Arabic)"
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 683325.0,
      "end_time": 685900.0,
      "text": "Laura Boushnak: He said, \"My dream is to run,"
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 685924.0,
      "end_time": 688101.0,
      "text": "and I&#39;m pretty sure once I start running,"
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 688125.0,
      "end_time": 689635.0,
      "text": "I would never stop.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 689659.0,
      "end_time": 690842.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 690866.0,
      "end_time": 695689.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}